Powers.DescLong: The SpecOps Combat assault rifle, or SCAR, can be used as a Sniper Rifle to take out a target at extreme range.

You blend into your environment and can only be seen at very close range. Even if discovered, you are hard to see and have a bonus to Defense from melee and ranged attacks. If, however, you attack while using this power, you will be discovered and will lose your Stealth and some of your Defense bonus. Stealth will not work with any other form of Concealment power such as Shadow Fall or Steamy Mist.  Very low Endurance cost.
The Tear Gas is making you choke.  Your Damage is Debuffed.
